{"title":"Colecistitis aguda-2024","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/Cirugía/Colecistitis aguda-2024.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Colecistitis\\Naguda","guid":"jKnZQ2CZP7AcpfnGM-N_FQ","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"1. Definición:","guid":"r-_hSRqjpqXm4PmD7FrBbg","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"• Inflamación aguda de la vesícula biliar (VB) →\\NFrecuentemente por obstrucción del conducto\\Ncístico (CC) por un cálculo biliar (Colecistitis\\Ncalculosa aguda - CCA).","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"3","parent":"0","text":"2. Epidemiología:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"4","parent":"3","text":"• Sexo: ♀ > ♂.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"5","parent":"3","text":"• Prevalencia: Complicación\\N+frec de la colelitiasis.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"6","parent":"3","text":"• Pico de\\Nincidencia: >50\\Naños.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"7","parent":"0","text":"3. Etiología:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"8","parent":"7","text":"• CCA (90%):","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"9","parent":"7","text":"• Obstrucción por colelitiasis →\\NDistensión e inflamación de VB.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"10","parent":"7","text":"• Infección bacteriana secundaria (+frec:\\NE. coli, Klebsiella spp., Enterobacter spp.\\N, Enterococcus spp.).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"11","parent":"7","text":"• Colecistitis\\Nacalculosa\\N(5-10%):","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"12","parent":"7","text":"• Asociada a pacientes\\Ncríticamente enfermos.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"13","parent":"7","text":"• Ver sección\\N“Acalculous\\Ncholecystitis”.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"14","parent":"0","text":"4. Cuadro Clínico:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"15","parent":"14","text":"• Dolor en cuadrante\\Nsuperior derecho (CSD).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"16","parent":"14","text":"• Signo de Murphy (+).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"17","parent":"14","text":"• Fiebre.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"18","parent":"0","text":"5. Diagnóstico:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"19","parent":"18","text":"• Ecografía RUQ:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"20","parent":"18","text":"• Distensión VB, edema,\\Nlíquido pericolecístico.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"21","parent":"18","text":"• Laboratorio:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"22","parent":"18","text":"• ↑ Leucocitosis, ↑ PCR.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"23","parent":"0","text":"6. Tratamiento:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"24","parent":"23","text":"• Antibioterapia empírica.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"25","parent":"23","text":"• Colecistectomía\\Nlaparoscópica:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"26","parent":"23","text":"• Realizar en <72\\Nhrs si es posible.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"27","parent":"23","text":"• Pacientes de alto riesgo: drenaje temporizador\\N(colecistostomía percutánea, stent endoscópico)\\N→ Colecistectomía electiva tras resolución de\\Nsíntomas agudos.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"28","parent":"0","text":"7. Complicaciones:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"29","parent":"28","text":"• Colecistitis\\Ngangrenosa,\\Nenfisematosa.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"30","parent":"28","text":"• Perforación VB.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"31","parent":"28","text":"• Fístula biliodigestiva.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"32","parent":"28","text":"• Íleo biliar.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"33","parent":"28","text":"• Absceso\\Nhepático\\Npiógeno.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"34","parent":"28","text":"• Colecistitis crónica → Riesgo ↑\\Nde carcinoma de VB.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"35","parent":"0","text":"Características\\NClínicas","guid":"BUbO2iSuEvWKZ7dCY2j6Bw","children":[{"id":"36","parent":"35","text":"1. Dolor en cuadrante\\Nsuperior derecho (CSD):","guid":"","children":[{"id":"37","parent":"36","text":"• +Severo y prolongado (>6 hrs) que en cólico biliar.","guid":"BWAveBXlyKC-ssvEUc8-cg","children":[]},{"id":"38","parent":"36","text":"• Postprandial.","guid":"ATcLh1HwFCr5TQiDBZ_1LQ","children":[{"id":"39","parent":"38","text":"• Irradiación a escápula derecha (dolor referido por irritación del nervio frénico).","guid":"eyDMRyIXFmoZJJl_gT4Xeg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"40","parent":"35","text":"2. Signo de Murphy (+):","guid":"","children":[{"id":"41","parent":"40","text":"• Pausa súbita en inspiración profunda con palpación del CSD por dolor.","guid":"QQPEGqGXzH8wREj8QQktAg","children":[]},{"id":"42","parent":"40","text":"• Falsos negativos en >60 años (n=5)(n=6).","guid":"WhVUyQztN25XYv9bOWafjw","children":[]}]},{"id":"43","parent":"35","text":"3. Defensa abdominal.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"44","parent":"35","text":"4. Fiebre, malestar general, anorexia.","guid":"5Er1KX-BCvgG04lseCrOAg","children":[]},{"id":"45","parent":"35","text":"5. Náuseas y vómitos.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"46","parent":"0","text":"Subtipos y\\NVariantes","guid":"7K18DgWQkx7soPaBqfyalw","children":[{"id":"47","parent":"46","text":"1. Colecistitis\\Nacalculosa aguda:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"48","parent":"47","text":"• Descripción: Trastorno necrinflamatorio agudo y grave de la VB, sin cálculos biliares.","guid":"I_qxo3rSEnQnINDwwRjnsQ","children":[]},{"id":"49","parent":"47","text":"• Incidencia: 5-10% de las colecistitis agudas (n=3).","guid":"oTCLsc-51Pogo02U9xsXuA","children":[]},{"id":"50","parent":"47","text":"• Etiología: Estasis biliar y ↓ perfusión de VB.","guid":"h4hesMl6h2yXdExyxQxKLA","children":[]},{"id":"51","parent":"47","text":"• Factores de riesgo:","guid":"gH8kMSh5J679Kn72F1viwA","children":[{"id":"52","parent":"51","text":"• Fallo multiorgánico.","guid":"hgWEbj1YDL0K9NchVSkIlw","children":[]},{"id":"53","parent":"51","text":"• Trauma grave, quemaduras.","guid":"Nzf1kBSxV2z5yPPf7c2u8Q","children":[]},{"id":"54","parent":"51","text":"• Cirugía.","guid":"AbaOgJeikp3abrauWnxVsg","children":[]},{"id":"55","parent":"51","text":"• Infecciones (CMV).","guid":"d91zIgB-LoEyq7KfRkIG-A","children":[]},{"id":"56","parent":"51","text":"• Sepsis, shock séptico.","guid":"RCOdw48HgvxcqUdpyAhiqg","children":[]},{"id":"57","parent":"51","text":"• Nutrición parenteral total.","guid":"-XPMRimeu5d1byYlUhYCAA","children":[]},{"id":"58","parent":"51","text":"• Ayuno prolongado.","guid":"Lyg2j9aFvlHsRY3iGCNgMA","children":[]},{"id":"59","parent":"51","text":"• Inmunodeficiencia.","guid":"i0KhrIvtudizrwpYyrjuzg","children":[]}]},{"id":"60","parent":"47","text":"• Clínica: Similar a colecistitis calculosa aguda.","guid":"S2rPe8gvAPiyRsOBCc9LdA","children":[]},{"id":"61","parent":"47","text":"• Diagnóstico:","guid":"y51IQmAqhkyGFIW9td6-IA","children":[{"id":"62","parent":"61","text":"• Estudios de laboratorio: Similares a colecistitis calculosa.","guid":"T_bN8rzEzPzXIIg_ZqIpwA","children":[]}]},{"id":"63","parent":"47","text":"• Imágenes:","guid":"1O1kHyillQU8VJHLiBmvUw","children":[{"id":"64","parent":"63","text":"• Ecografía abdominal: Engrosamiento pared VB\\N(>3-5 mm), líquido pericolecístico, sin litiasis\\Nvisible (puede haber lodo biliar).","guid":"ohS1Ss5WNgRoH_MOpV7czQ","children":[]},{"id":"65","parent":"63","text":"• Gammagrafía HIDA: Confirmatoria si\\Necografía no concluyente.","guid":"pROg1R7zlkDEgjbZwmShRQ","children":[]},{"id":"66","parent":"63","text":"• TAC abdominal con contraste IV:\\NAlternativa si ecografía no concluyente.","guid":"nlZc1o6srCNx-VJjQ6x3eQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"67","parent":"47","text":"• Tratamiento:","guid":"mT6xXaVwdsNB2EfwmC9gUw","children":[{"id":"68","parent":"67","text":"• Manejo inicial: NPO, líquidos IV, analgésicos.","guid":"SIC-TkIBj186sJHiHRCesg","children":[]},{"id":"69","parent":"67","text":"• Antibióticos IV.","guid":"7nu8hwX46p31YliZomGu2g","children":[]},{"id":"70","parent":"67","text":"• Control de fuente:","guid":"aWowCKXoky8istcPDEHWLQ","children":[{"id":"71","parent":"70","text":"• Pacientes de bajo riesgo: Colecistectomía laparoscópica de emergencia.","guid":"9JbDVsnqeEbhg1_y6uF26g","children":[]},{"id":"72","parent":"70","text":"• Pacientes de alto riesgo: Colecistostomía percutánea.","guid":"EGpVXDMmhbdsMaTgXwt-WA","children":[]},{"id":"73","parent":"70","text":"• Si no mejora en 2-3 días → Colecistectomía (n=9).","guid":"npVkvmTGinv7eI6XXvXZdw","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"74","parent":"46","text":"2. Colecistitis\\Nenfisematosa (CE):","guid":"","children":[{"id":"75","parent":"74","text":"• Descripción: Forma rara pero grave de colecistitis aguda con gas en la pared o\\Nlumen de la VB por bacterias formadoras de gas (Clostridium spp., E. coli).","guid":"igmpH1ybuorYByQP1LdsZA","children":[]},{"id":"76","parent":"74","text":"• Epidemiología: Rara; +frec en hombres mayores con DM (50-70 años) (n=12).","guid":"ZhfQnXcHCk-oC5WtWaMujw","children":[]},{"id":"77","parent":"74","text":"• Fisiopatología:","guid":"MA45caq-lYDqTCAebwlkkQ","children":[{"id":"78","parent":"77","text":"• Compromiso vascular primario (oclusión arteria cística) → Isquemia de pared VB\\N→ Necrosis → Proliferación de bacterias formadoras de gas.","guid":"mfLhNH3P02EqcQz7OX7FHw","children":[]}]},{"id":"79","parent":"74","text":"• Patógenos +frec: Clostridium spp., E. coli.","guid":"Zbt5jluk65nNZOoEQWXlZA","children":[]},{"id":"80","parent":"74","text":"• Factores de riesgo:","guid":"JVOtN0jFa_m7XMQdlkITpQ","children":[{"id":"81","parent":"80","text":"• Hiperglicemia (DM).","guid":"lO0vwbjNv2EaRkaWlQiHFw","children":[]},{"id":"82","parent":"80","text":"• Inmunosupresión.","guid":"qR0_L40Q69wNUAqou9aQRg","children":[]},{"id":"83","parent":"80","text":"• Enfermedades vasculares (aterosclerosis, embolia arterial, vasculitis).","guid":"hPaU01r-EFA0lI0R4EnMWw","children":[]},{"id":"84","parent":"80","text":"• Cirugía abdominal, trauma.","guid":"MZOgMYaK5LB15G0c1COY5Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"85","parent":"74","text":"• Clínica:","guid":"BcUXt-_R85VVThp2XMVj5g","children":[{"id":"86","parent":"85","text":"• Similar a colecistitis calculosa aguda.","guid":"hvCz2VE9IuiwDyi4DCmmNQ","children":[]},{"id":"87","parent":"85","text":"• Síntomas progresan rápidamente.","guid":"BZbo22nW6YQ8_7g8gLYvZw","children":[]},{"id":"88","parent":"85","text":"• Asociado a gangrena temprana y perforación VB.","guid":"pSV2PbUDfRn5pf__42ynng","children":[]}]},{"id":"89","parent":"74","text":"• Diagnóstico:","guid":"6Ixq9-N3NnA3_9-0zsbPPw","children":[{"id":"90","parent":"89","text":"• Laboratorio: Similares a colecistitis calculosa.","guid":"xR2m6UnPcTnAuIiZA5N8uA","children":[]},{"id":"91","parent":"89","text":"• Imágenes:","guid":"N6PUUzbw9ngnQC5ps8GY1w","children":[{"id":"92","parent":"91","text":"• Ecografía RUQ: Sombras hiperecoicas de aire en pared VB, y en bilis de lumen VB.","guid":"1zLmQ8UOg7bJhH5YBD_kjA","children":[]},{"id":"93","parent":"91","text":"• TAC abdomen sin contraste: Sombras radiolúcidas en pared VB, bilis, y líquido pericolecístico.","guid":"Ce4M_8dhJSdKmNqDpSdirQ","children":[]},{"id":"94","parent":"91","text":"• RM abdomen: Áreas hipointensas (vacío de señal) en pared VB.","guid":"TOx9ftLgrNWgmLYiUf_w2A","children":[]},{"id":"95","parent":"91","text":"• RX abdomen: Borde radiolúcido en contorno VB (radiolucencia en forma de pera).","guid":"ipbazErml95lkwOi3zdQ-g","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"96","parent":"74","text":"• Tratamiento:","guid":"cxGrxHXsv5BvV2PuG1zkSw","children":[{"id":"97","parent":"96","text":"• Manejo inicial: NPO, líquidos IV, analgésicos.","guid":"eos-YMEEJB93WfITtZvFQw","children":[]},{"id":"98","parent":"96","text":"• Antibióticos IV de amplio espectro con cobertura para anaerobios.","guid":"xLpPfhF-0aTA2eTvqrf3nA","children":[]},{"id":"99","parent":"96","text":"• Procedimiento de control de\\Nfuente de emergencia:","guid":"d9d7TL57mKcH2T56OdDvHA","children":[{"id":"100","parent":"99","text":"• Pacientes de bajo riesgo: Colecistectomía laparoscópica de emergencia.","guid":"Pc34AGLYt64nrFAvXLIpqg","children":[]},{"id":"101","parent":"99","text":"• Pacientes de alto riesgo: Drenaje VB (n=12)(n=14).","guid":"CK9POBCkMalXg0I4mx2y_w","children":[]}]}]}]}]},{"id":"102","parent":"0","text":"Diagnóstico de\\NColecistitis Aguda","guid":"OBgiZ_puOwMQfrZDZpJ1IA","children":[{"id":"103","parent":"102","text":"1. Criterios\\NDiagnósticos:","guid":"zQkgiFXaDcZwIVNMRWcc9w","children":[{"id":"104","parent":"103","text":"• Signos locales de\\Ninflamación:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"105","parent":"104","text":"• Signo de Murphy.","guid":"V8FQ3EPEcCsJMBwTa7Rz9w","children":[]},{"id":"106","parent":"104","text":"• Dolor, sensibilidad o masa en CSD.","guid":"H6G-CTEdbuU10DtH2ObzEg","children":[]}]},{"id":"107","parent":"103","text":"• Signos sistémicos\\Nde inflamación:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"108","parent":"107","text":"• Fiebre.","guid":"zre3Y-DCIi4QDx2YuXcBRw","children":[]},{"id":"109","parent":"107","text":"• ↑ CRP.","guid":"5d0JF1Y-dPMUg5io65sJ_Q","children":[]},{"id":"110","parent":"107","text":"• Leucocitosis.","guid":"FMJvGjQYbv1j_tEGEx0tZw","children":[]},{"id":"111","parent":"107","text":"• Hallazgos en imágenes:","guid":"1ohfbnj_sT1DlJTsYg8ZBg","children":[]}]},{"id":"112","parent":"103","text":"• Cualquier hallazgo característico de colecistitis aguda\\N(ver sección de “Imágenes”).","guid":"HnG7AvmnQa20lQYoyUA5Tw","children":[]},{"id":"113","parent":"103","text":"• Interpretación:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"114","parent":"113","text":"• Dx sospechado: ≥ 1 signo local de inflamación\\N+ ≥ 1 signo sistémico de inflamación.","guid":"oEwspudrgdQk3ZOuokNycA","children":[]},{"id":"115","parent":"113","text":"• Dx definitivo: ≥ 1 signo local de inflamación + ≥ 1 signo sistémico de inflamación\\N+ hallazgo característico en imágenes (n=11).","guid":"KA__mO4dpfOzL_Biqp84LA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"116","parent":"102","text":"2. Evaluación\\NInicial:","guid":"YV5Ajeia3F9jajmPEEisJg","children":[{"id":"117","parent":"116","text":"• Laboratorio:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"118","parent":"117","text":"• CBC: Leucocitosis (+frec) pero leucocitos normales en hasta 40% (n=15).","guid":"cJEIS7GKMNFIlQtsjlrVQg","children":[]},{"id":"119","parent":"117","text":"• CRP: Elevada.","guid":"IF6Ru-6pb3uagFOA0JqyaQ","children":[]},{"id":"120","parent":"117","text":"• Hemocultivos: Obtener en colecistitis aguda grado III (n=17).","guid":"PoErrxabx1HlKpMXPGsDBg","children":[]},{"id":"121","parent":"117","text":"• Cultivo de bilis: Indicado en colecistectomía laparoscópica o drenaje VB (n=17).","guid":"HZC5NoLpwjcNCoer9LshKg","children":[]}]},{"id":"122","parent":"116","text":"• Imágenes:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"123","parent":"122","text":"• Ecografía\\Ntransabdominal RUQ:","guid":"ugIjoCOnDEwyhS6_8V-lug","children":[{"id":"124","parent":"123","text":"• Indicaciones: Modalidad de imagen inicial preferida (n=10).","guid":"efrESIyF-aZoMpAjQu5IiA","children":[]},{"id":"125","parent":"123","text":"• Hallazgos\\Ncaracterísticos:","guid":"L1UMme8TU9_afxqUf1TbSg","children":[{"id":"126","parent":"125","text":"• Engrosamiento de pared VB > 3-5 mm (n=8).","guid":"EVQPFkg-FGWCyZyJhwLIQg","children":[]},{"id":"127","parent":"125","text":"• Distensión VB (8-10 x 4 cm) (n=11)(n=20).","guid":"5mswYYsrgZifcb6lk15lWw","children":[]},{"id":"128","parent":"125","text":"• Edema de pared VB (signo de doble pared).","guid":"D23wC-YqtO_cvkHfzloDBA","children":[]},{"id":"129","parent":"125","text":"• Signo de Murphy sonográfico.","guid":"SIOE9LE-nH7L92-XHVe5og","children":[]},{"id":"130","parent":"125","text":"• Líquido pericolecístico.","guid":"BHOR0lvQb29RPKHM5mQo-A","children":[]},{"id":"131","parent":"125","text":"• Presencia de cálculos biliares y/o lodo biliar.","guid":"PXn34J6l08Zk1K2wGFpPSQ","children":[]},{"id":"132","parent":"125","text":"• Aire mural en colecistitis enfisematosa (n=8).","guid":"rfwguXFXNnTOIwBQd7s5BA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"133","parent":"122","text":"• Gammagrafía\\NHIDA:","guid":"2it4MgHrgRsR52G9HFDqHg","children":[{"id":"134","parent":"133","text":"• Indicaciones: Confirmatoria en caso de ecografía no concluyente.","guid":"Wp-B6lZEqLzOlrzxCWnIkg","children":[]},{"id":"135","parent":"133","text":"• Procedimiento: Inyección de 99mTc-HIDA → captación selectiva por hepatocitos\\N→ excreción en bilis → VB no visualizada en 4 hrs indica colecistitis aguda.","guid":"py_RxRpRjTlaHEM8sxdZnA","children":[]},{"id":"136","parent":"133","text":"• Ventajas: Alta sensibilidad (96%) y especificidad (90%);\\Nestándar de oro (n=21)(n=22).","guid":"N8vwukgxkYYpEngTdQT1dA","children":[]},{"id":"137","parent":"133","text":"• Desventajas: Toma tiempo, no evalúa complicaciones, disponibilidad limitada.","guid":"o9ct_BCnSA7c7m8qM5BgfQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"138","parent":"122","text":"• RMN abdomen con\\Ny sin contraste:","guid":"K6OoNmZHYIkL-GxEIvA1yQ","children":[{"id":"139","parent":"138","text":"• Indicaciones: Alternativa a TAC o HIDA en ecografía no concluyente.","guid":"ZyvW-d6dv4mV8lLCb5e66g","children":[]},{"id":"140","parent":"138","text":"• Hallazgos característicos: Hiperintensidad (T2) de pared VB y región pericolecística, indicando inflamación.\\NEvidencia de complicaciones (colecistitis enfisematosa, empiema VB, perforación VB) (n=10)(n=20)(n=23).","guid":"regDkrnCU8PVmbpUjz0NiA","children":[]}]},{"id":"141","parent":"122","text":"• TAC abdomen\\Ncon contraste IV:","guid":"z0sD_zwgLW1lvhgrOdYCvw","children":[{"id":"142","parent":"141","text":"• Indicaciones: Alternativa a RMN o HIDA en ecografía no concluyente.\\NSospecha de colecistitis enfisematosa o complicaciones.","guid":"iH12Nw90xlnf8GfXm9AGqA","children":[]},{"id":"143","parent":"141","text":"• Hallazgos: Similares a ecografía y RMN (n=8)(n=11)(n=3).","guid":"wPfhaawoKT8wQUGmnMqi-A","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"144","parent":"102","text":"3. Evaluación de\\Nseveridad:","guid":"i1bCHXlZUI1AeHAD-epsmw","children":[{"id":"145","parent":"144","text":"• Análisis de gasometría: PaO2/FiO2 < 300 en pacientes gravemente enfermos.","guid":"k9NTZivgmy4RX-dJ2R_kpg","children":[]},{"id":"146","parent":"144","text":"• BMP: IRA, desequilibrios electrolíticos en enfermedad severa.","guid":"A_ZN1Mbu3X45vHF6EFXHJw","children":[]},{"id":"147","parent":"144","text":"• PT/INR: Coagulopatía en enfermedad severa.","guid":"i7_ro70onfGY57Ye3-xA8A","children":[]}]},{"id":"148","parent":"102","text":"4. Diagnósticos\\NDiferenciales:","guid":"KY6OCS1LSQ4aqAQiYYajig","children":[{"id":"149","parent":"148","text":"• Realizar pruebas para descartar comorbilidades biliares relacionadas.","guid":"DYnQ0UdQgrWSfBkDD6Qj0g","children":[]},{"id":"150","parent":"148","text":"• LFTs: Elevación leve de AST y ALT. Elevación de bilirrubina, ALP, y GGT raros, sugieren obstrucción biliar.","guid":"mQB8pkjIvQYz_pmL86zg5A","children":[]},{"id":"151","parent":"148","text":"• Lipasa, amilasa: Elevación leve de amilasa en colecistitis aguda. Lipasa o amilasa ≥ 3x normal sugiere pancreatitis biliar aguda (n=19).","guid":"EL5yEsDLwzeAedEca6QQQw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"152","parent":"0","text":"Diagnósticos Diferenciales\\Nde Colecistitis Aguda","guid":"3MV1_MlgcgF3cD3QzEh9Bw","children":[{"id":"153","parent":"152","text":"1. Dolor en CSD\\Ncon fiebre:","guid":"lG2p71eVJRFPCYRUWdjdaQ","children":[{"id":"154","parent":"153","text":"• Colangitis aguda.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"155","parent":"153","text":"• Absceso hepático.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"156","parent":"153","text":"• Hepatitis aguda.","guid":"t1sOBB5O7KuzL30rzkyArg","children":[]},{"id":"157","parent":"153","text":"• Pancreatitis necrotizante aguda.","guid":"4l78kmiOG9LQvo9GxiHcew","children":[]},{"id":"158","parent":"153","text":"• Colecistitis acalculosa.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"159","parent":"153","text":"• Colecistitis crónica.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"160","parent":"153","text":"• Fuga biliar (iatrogénica).","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"161","parent":"152","text":"2. Dolor en CSD\\Nsin fiebre:","guid":"lrU_ei19OSeiCAqzgM_uig","children":[{"id":"162","parent":"161","text":"• Cólico biliar.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"163","parent":"161","text":"• Úlcera péptica (PUD).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"164","parent":"161","text":"• Gastritis aguda.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"165","parent":"161","text":"• Pancreatitis aguda.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"166","parent":"161","text":"• Pancreatitis crónica.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"167","parent":"161","text":"• ERGE aguda.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"168","parent":"161","text":"• Disfunción del esfínter de Oddi.","guid":"atDtPrqGcX4tzAkn6x2a9g","children":[]},{"id":"169","parent":"161","text":"• Hepatopatía congestiva.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"170","parent":"161","text":"• Nefrolitiasis.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"171","parent":"161","text":"• Neoplasias:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"172","parent":"161","text":"• Carcinoma hepatocelular (HCC).","guid":"9t6N-71ubDoMxQQbKae0AQ","children":[]},{"id":"173","parent":"161","text":"• Colangiocarcinoma.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"174","parent":"161","text":"• Cáncer de vesícula biliar.","guid":"lop20Db9Dk--4rZYHeRwzw","children":[]},{"id":"175","parent":"161","text":"• Cáncer de páncreas.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"176","parent":"152","text":"3. Evaluación de severidad\\Nde colecistitis aguda:","guid":"uKT6fFibY0JosWzrC56efg","children":[{"id":"177","parent":"176","text":"• Grado I (leve):","guid":"_zITGnKnkm9fwTvOYcbyyw","children":[{"id":"178","parent":"177","text":"• Sin disfunción orgánica ni enfermedad grave de VB.","guid":"AUk1_QItd3YB8EbaQuiQpw","children":[]},{"id":"179","parent":"177","text":"• No cumple criterios de grado II o III.","guid":"96ZJkuHaKYQDOskkfottaQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"180","parent":"176","text":"• Grado II (moderada):","guid":"Iv4rZFcpIJEwg279hOINnQ","children":[{"id":"181","parent":"180","text":"• Sin disfunción orgánica.","guid":"aHbbdXXre3HR21SYle_XfA","children":[]},{"id":"182","parent":"180","text":"• Al menos uno de los siguientes signos de enfermedad grave de VB:","guid":"39JVWHPSiWXb5WhkD-dC8Q","children":[]},{"id":"183","parent":"180","text":"• Duración de síntomas > 72 hrs.","guid":"KQ_7whCJvhgmb9uxT0kWQA","children":[]},{"id":"184","parent":"180","text":"• Leucocitos > 18,000/mm³.","guid":"o7wr_-vvkymALTR_frmyHg","children":[]},{"id":"185","parent":"180","text":"• Masa palpable en CSD.","guid":"xxSFKDkEEoug-nfiRReArA","children":[]},{"id":"186","parent":"180","text":"• Signos de inflamación local significativa en estudios de imagen.","guid":"odBbe-65AJBb676t-z5mtw","children":[]}]},{"id":"187","parent":"176","text":"• Grado III (severa):","guid":"6mLTaoQEodshYE8bkYBFyQ","children":[{"id":"188","parent":"187","text":"• Disfunción de al menos\\Nun sistema orgánico:","guid":"EFdR9hgRMDBAMXBmrKWB2A","children":[{"id":"189","parent":"188","text":"• Cardiovascular: Hipotensión que requiere dopamina ≥ 5 mcg/kg/min\\No cualquier dosis de norepinefrina.","guid":"nj9-8RAmqUWwbj_9aspZnA","children":[]}]},{"id":"190","parent":"187","text":"• Neurológico: Conciencia alterada.","guid":"2-4r0mwPhnpmi1CodddQrA","children":[]},{"id":"191","parent":"187","text":"• Respiratorio: PaO2/FiO2 < 300.","guid":"0_08NM2CKIfbWXW2rJCgDg","children":[]},{"id":"192","parent":"187","text":"• Renal: Oliguria, creatinina sérica > 2 mg/dl.","guid":"QFg_GSBLMEcIcquf0L-MZQ","children":[]},{"id":"193","parent":"187","text":"• Hepático: INR > 1.5.","guid":"ycglM7bdjXds7JkM5wd-pg","children":[]},{"id":"194","parent":"187","text":"• Hematológico: Plaquetas < 100, 000/mm³.","guid":"gdLRAz7EEHALi2XJeDiNYA","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"195","parent":"0","text":"Tratamiento de\\NColecistitis Aguda","guid":"93mFCqeMf1PflFAE-TBQyg","children":[{"id":"196","parent":"195","text":"1. Manejo Inicial:","guid":"4xCFcb_wHiJgwJODkuLrcw","children":[{"id":"197","parent":"196","text":"• Evaluación\\Ninicial:","guid":"kSseyAdk-yAjmPg8qzQFQw","children":[{"id":"198","parent":"197","text":"• Evaluar signos de sepsis o shock.","guid":"FOQQo0Q1zldGSe1IGMyzyQ","children":[]},{"id":"199","parent":"197","text":"• Proporcionar soporte hemodinámico inmediato (e. g., fluidoterapia IV)\\Ny soporte respiratorio (e.g., oxigenoterapia) si es necesario.","guid":"YRTiTeGpyd6FUZoN1wgboQ","children":[]},{"id":"200","parent":"197","text":"• Iniciar antibióticos empíricos para infección biliar aguda.","guid":"rc9INtlLycDS36dEc3u98g","children":[]}]},{"id":"201","parent":"196","text":"• Terapia de\\Nsoporte inicial:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"202","parent":"201","text":"• Analgesia.","guid":"OkqqarBoRtTrVWv2hlfpxA","children":[]},{"id":"203","parent":"201","text":"• Antieméticos.","guid":"FXyU6PyA_-xLU1H-G5o3wA","children":[]},{"id":"204","parent":"201","text":"• Reposición electrolítica.","guid":"Kt613k-FmKqa0jEo5KMQ0Q","children":[]},{"id":"205","parent":"201","text":"• Considerar inserción de sonda NG.","guid":"MBRcy0hAMqv-VchD5p56qA","children":[]},{"id":"206","parent":"201","text":"• Mantener estado NPO.","guid":"a6yU3edFQVypOYqe6YAQJA","children":[]}]},{"id":"207","parent":"196","text":"• Consultar a cirugía\\Ngeneral para:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"208","parent":"207","text":"• Evaluar riesgo quirúrgico (ASA-PS o índice de comorbilidad de Charlson - CCI).","guid":"Qf12yLi6e1cGHfd6f4Eh7Q","children":[]},{"id":"209","parent":"207","text":"• Determinar manejo definitivo según severidad y riesgo de complicaciones","guid":"hu2zfXw6PoCQnwWFI0l9UQ","children":[]},{"id":"210","parent":"207","text":"• Identificar y tratar coledocolitiasis concurrente","guid":"nju__-Y0JWCtcWTeVLsD4g","children":[]}]},{"id":"211","parent":"196","text":"• Monitoreo y\\Nreevaluación:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"212","parent":"211","text":"• Ajustar nivel de monitoreo según necesidades del paciente.","guid":"VvELMEIl-pnS7WFkFyyblg","children":[]},{"id":"213","parent":"211","text":"• Si hay deterioro temprano, realizar evaluación ABCDE.","guid":"RFdN89q8roVa-5SmREZpEg","children":[]},{"id":"214","parent":"211","text":"• Considerar desarrollo de complicaciones (e.g., perforación de vesícula biliar) u\\Notros diagnósticos diferenciales (e.g., colangitis aguda).","guid":"M3qfqZ2tKECoA6BTkcN1uQ","children":[]},{"id":"215","parent":"211","text":"• Considerar consulta a UCI.","guid":"qLNLvsHM1KG0Hj6_ZeNGrg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"216","parent":"195","text":"2. Manejo Definitivo:","guid":"yGfHh7wLu6kfJd8fT-4kmQ","children":[{"id":"217","parent":"216","text":"• Colecistectomía\\Nlaparoscópica:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"218","parent":"217","text":"• Enfoque preferido si hay experiencia disponible.","guid":"uTVW-BafSRIjsVwn_2IQdg","children":[]},{"id":"219","parent":"217","text":"• Realizar lo antes posible, a menos que los riesgos quirúrgicos/anestésicos superen los beneficios.","guid":"0nEqqb0lBqwvGFwhJkC1ig","children":[]},{"id":"220","parent":"217","text":"• Conversión a colecistectomía abierta puede ser necesaria según hallazgos intraoperatorios.","guid":"ma97CEQmfqahlrXYDVlF9A","children":[]}]},{"id":"221","parent":"216","text":"• Procedimientos de drenaje de vesícula biliar\\N(e.g., colecistostomía percutánea):","guid":"fpoZ3MHppupBYZ7PWO4XMA","children":[{"id":"222","parent":"221","text":"• Medida temporal en pacientes inestables o en deterioro clínico (grado II-III).","guid":"ddwhtc37OjdrSxMb9mEUJw","children":[]},{"id":"223","parent":"221","text":"• Pacientes frágiles o con alto riesgo de complicaciones quirúrgicas.","guid":"lr3YDwJqyqLTNXEMWFnGpw","children":[]}]},{"id":"224","parent":"216","text":"• Antibióticos\\Npostprocedimiento:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"225","parent":"224","text":"• Prolongar\\Nterapia si:","guid":"DpyTrf8KDZi8HhnVL0V6Yg","children":[{"id":"226","parent":"225","text":"• Signos de sepsis (e.g., fiebre persistente, leucocitosis estable o en aumento).","guid":"FME7BMZvWi4FZfoYIuYguA","children":[]},{"id":"227","parent":"225","text":"• Evidencia de obstrucción del tracto biliar.","guid":"s_6JK3OuyYZBeoRZdjqzxw","children":[]},{"id":"228","parent":"225","text":"• Complicaciones (e.g., absceso pericolecístico).","guid":"orKMbSCIVYG3dQneZWJCPQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"229","parent":"224","text":"• Ajustar antibióticos según cultivos de bilis y/o sangre.","guid":"o9JqaSV4zsXgW5BQ5aD7jw","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"230","parent":"0","text":"3. Manejo según\\NGrado de Severidad:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"231","parent":"230","text":"• Colecistitis aguda\\Ngrado I (leve):","guid":"","children":[{"id":"232","parent":"231","text":"• Bajo riesgo quirúrgico:","guid":"n49sqA_bE-bka4ndZ-1h5A","children":[{"id":"233","parent":"232","text":"• Colecistectomía laparoscópica temprana.","guid":"RVcxnLJLlmAaISst_BGa5Q","children":[]},{"id":"234","parent":"232","text":"• Antibióticos postoperatorios no requeridos.","guid":"EwDOqNXxFsccoJYXuHokmA","children":[]}]},{"id":"235","parent":"231","text":"• Alto riesgo quirúrgico:","guid":"VACH-bGqvRMJD_fVjGEk4g","children":[{"id":"236","parent":"235","text":"• Intervención temprana:","guid":"S2UR_S67HuGHYCr5afMJsQ","children":[{"id":"237","parent":"236","text":"• Colecistectomía laparoscópica temprana.","guid":"ow6XjOUMOKIcMSblfCE55Q","children":[]},{"id":"238","parent":"236","text":"• Discontinuar antibióticos 24 hrs después de la cirugía.","guid":"j25ubXUl_1DHUrZgCAqvxw","children":[]}]},{"id":"239","parent":"235","text":"• Enfoque conservador:","guid":"wCUKY9iZavcuW2pZHE1Waw","children":[{"id":"240","parent":"239","text":"• Continuar antibióticos hasta mejoría sintomática.","guid":"ZzeffModY_2a_qUPN6_hsA","children":[]},{"id":"241","parent":"239","text":"• Programar colecistectomía intervalada.","guid":"P2wImYw1wVBau1rb2T7KvA","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"242","parent":"230","text":"• Colecistitis aguda\\Ngrado II (moderada):","guid":"","children":[{"id":"243","parent":"242","text":"• Mejoría con\\Nmanejo inicial:","guid":"wUwIKhNh9nOENZjO2IBvMA","children":[{"id":"244","parent":"243","text":"• Bajo riesgo quirúrgico:","guid":"2d2w9qYT3-M9skKsA-D8Kg","children":[{"id":"245","parent":"244","text":"• Colecistectomía laparoscópica temprana.","guid":"JhgjNVf88Ryq4LxNYlMx-g","children":[]},{"id":"246","parent":"244","text":"• Discontinuar antibióticos 24 hrs después de la cirugía.","guid":"jY2Q5MgLs2NjFXG_c1TTTQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"247","parent":"243","text":"• Alto riesgo quirúrgico:","guid":"jHZAKkYoMKRinTBn4Fbe4Q","children":[{"id":"248","parent":"247","text":"• Continuar antibióticos hasta mejoría sintomática.","guid":"svf05YHNz7msklstlnobPg","children":[]},{"id":"249","parent":"247","text":"• Programar colecistectomía intervalada.","guid":"U2qEka_BUFagd8aBpJMmKw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"250","parent":"242","text":"• Deterioro a pesar del\\Nmanejo inicial:","guid":"m4XpuaJX05VOlpEHBORLQw","children":[{"id":"251","parent":"250","text":"• Drenaje urgente de vesícula biliar seguido de colecistectomía intervalada.","guid":"PxFp52Dbt68wsTO7AK3-JQ","children":[]},{"id":"252","parent":"250","text":"• Continuar antibióticos por un total de 7 días.","guid":"XoVFQNkiC4ivFs9YPgN9IA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"253","parent":"230","text":"• Colecistitis aguda\\Ngrado III (severa):","guid":"CRxGcA-q9A3wLotZI8Zc_w","children":[{"id":"254","parent":"253","text":"• Bajo riesgo\\Nquirúrgico:","guid":"GuolAB7J1t9WBeo6yzvz8w","children":[{"id":"255","parent":"254","text":"• Colecistectomía laparoscópica temprana si hay respuesta adecuada al soporte inicial.","guid":"R_LN_s2rEdY9CY9IN_82dw","children":[]},{"id":"256","parent":"254","text":"• Continuar antibióticos por 4-7 días después de la cirugía.","guid":"IcCce6BR5AbmtnO6b970vw","children":[]}]},{"id":"257","parent":"253","text":"• Alto riesgo\\Nquirúrgico:","guid":"l3Jx9fQkxn5LgyEoXJw__Q","children":[{"id":"258","parent":"257","text":"• Drenaje urgente de\\Nvesícula biliar, seguido de:","guid":"tRaVirSdufdIJmwMREZuFA","children":[{"id":"259","parent":"258","text":"• Colecistectomía intervalada.","guid":"j4VFf2imlhV5r9HSv-sIDw","children":[]},{"id":"260","parent":"258","text":"• O observación.","guid":"weUGO4yUglzn6ELmXeIDcw","children":[]}]},{"id":"261","parent":"257","text":"• Continuar antibióticos por un total de 7 días.","guid":"52tpUh47Mq3-9GfTfap29w","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"262","parent":"0","text":"Procedimientos para\\NColecistitis Aguda","guid":"DKrWn0kNLfhi_xhnHdji6A","children":[{"id":"263","parent":"262","text":"1. Colecistectomía\\NLaparoscópica:","guid":"188qp8P_e2gqP6O8ZnzhUQ","children":[{"id":"264","parent":"263","text":"• Indicaciones:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"265","parent":"264","text":"• Estándar de oro para el tratamiento de la colecistitis calculosa aguda (n=24).","guid":"qBXapGedKH9CMX-Z4szHMQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"266","parent":"263","text":"• Momento:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"267","parent":"266","text":"• Depende de riesgos quirúrgicos y anestésicos, severidad de la enfermedad, y duración de síntomas.","guid":"avwGylwvR9lZOS_Wb0albQ","children":[]},{"id":"268","parent":"266","text":"• Colecistectomía\\Nlaparoscópica temprana:","guid":"0pegy78ZRyWe9Z3I2ZlppA","children":[{"id":"269","parent":"268","text":"• Realizada dentro de los 10 días desde el inicio de los síntomas; preferiblemente en las primeras 24-72 horas.","guid":"y1B0OFsB8-Z1ERIdzkx7BA","children":[]},{"id":"270","parent":"268","text":"• Indicaciones:","guid":"UsuKiRz_sYlI_jiwkZMYJg","children":[{"id":"271","parent":"270","text":"• Duración de síntomas ≤ 10 días en pacientes con bajo riesgo quirúrgico y anestésico.","guid":"d0P68heiVazj8pjOQUWx8A","children":[]}]},{"id":"272","parent":"268","text":"• Contraindicaciones:","guid":"JesG_GQoahs0TuDCkxeNgg","children":[{"id":"273","parent":"272","text":"• Alto riesgo quirúrgico o anestésico.","guid":"U71ksKdJMBZRUVzK-QARNA","children":[]},{"id":"274","parent":"272","text":"• Duración de síntomas > 10 días.","guid":"ejC2_qgeiPE2vslOEEqx2w","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"275","parent":"266","text":"• Colecistectomía laparoscópica\\Nintervalada:","guid":"aInyn4Fw5gscC-KXmYzeBw","children":[{"id":"276","parent":"275","text":"• Realizada 45 días después de la resolución de los síntomas.","guid":"9dvhMdXYpnHobOjn7jSlmQ","children":[]},{"id":"277","parent":"275","text":"• Indicaciones:","guid":"KDxcgmDMWvKabh3whs8ayQ","children":[{"id":"278","parent":"277","text":"• Alto riesgo quirúrgico o anestésico.","guid":"QB3-Tsj6wRt8iO60Jo4XhA","children":[]},{"id":"279","parent":"277","text":"• Duración de síntomas > 10 días.","guid":"kxF8UEvsPDxGQ9wnm0jrdQ","children":[]}]}]}]}]},{"id":"280","parent":"262","text":"2. Drenaje de\\NVesícula Biliar:","guid":"ZXBJPlDAn9Bb5_gMaFLpIg","children":[{"id":"281","parent":"280","text":"• Indicaciones:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"282","parent":"281","text":"• Medida temporal y mínimamente invasiva en pacientes de alto\\Nriesgo quirúrgico que no responden al manejo conservador (n=31).","guid":"rr6NjPI_Zq6I48fG6fynmw","children":[]}]},{"id":"283","parent":"280","text":"• Contraindicaciones:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"284","parent":"283","text":"• Diátesis hemorrágica no controlada.","guid":"h3CU4swbBVfZDu4b85-BRg","children":[]}]},{"id":"285","parent":"280","text":"• Opciones:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"286","parent":"285","text":"• Colecistostomía percutánea:","guid":"OC8LthC8SAx2aORkzh03wQ","children":[{"id":"287","parent":"286","text":"• Colocación de un catéter (tubo de colecistostomía) en la vesícula biliar bajo guía por imagen y\\Nanestesia local, a través de la pared abdominal, para proporcionar drenaje biliar (n=31)(n=32).","guid":"bNghkgaMQ7cedsq6G3jLVw","children":[]}]},{"id":"288","parent":"285","text":"• Colocación de stent endoscópico\\Nen la vesícula biliar:","guid":"Of0gU1_HncwxEHe27MKSgw","children":[{"id":"289","parent":"288","text":"• Puede preferirse sobre la colecistostomía percutánea si hay experiencia\\Nen endoscopia, ya que es menos invasiva (n=33)(n=34)(n=35).","guid":"1oNPZf9aIg8IkicMqqnKxQ","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"290","parent":"262","text":"3. Disposición:","guid":"ryzvatAIgVgF_auuVlOTzw","children":[{"id":"291","parent":"290","text":"• Todos los pacientes con colecistitis aguda requieren manejo intrahospitalario.","guid":"FVSJ8YjK7T3626jt4RhJOw","children":[]},{"id":"292","parent":"290","text":"• Colecistitis aguda grado I:","guid":"yZIfKbuHrJulyi63DKUoPg","children":[{"id":"293","parent":"292","text":"• Centro de salud con capacidad para realizar colecistectomía laparoscópica.","guid":"e0v8gN_-IOP5weOOTnN4rg","children":[]}]},{"id":"294","parent":"290","text":"• Colecistitis\\Naguda grado II:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"295","parent":"294","text":"• Centro de salud avanzado con acceso a drenaje urgente de vesícula biliar y\\Nexperiencia quirúrgica para manejar una colecistectomía laparoscópica difícil.","guid":"X7zxmxCFRYiK3FbPLnVuDQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"296","parent":"290","text":"• Colecistitis\\Naguda grado III:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"297","parent":"296","text":"• Igual que el grado II, MÁS acceso a\\Ncuidados intensivos (n=25).","guid":"iL-QzEa0GDcsHvMyEw2-Qw","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"298","parent":"0","text":"Terapia Antibiótica para\\NInfección Biliar Aguda","guid":"kD9HoHQTZMQghdVTUIy0og","children":[{"id":"299","parent":"298","text":"1. Principios\\NGenerales:","guid":"_iJodIJRcjenQ6XueuOTbw","children":[{"id":"300","parent":"299","text":"• Consideraciones\\Nimportantes:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"301","parent":"300","text":"• Obtener hemocultivos antes de administrar antibióticos, especialmente en pacientes con infección biliar grave.","guid":"eikxvC-pdnauNCcDJkYPig","children":[]},{"id":"302","parent":"300","text":"• Obtener cultivos de bilis al inicio de cualquier procedimiento de drenaje.","guid":"-7ITAyS-qGx3oy_um27Ygg","children":[]},{"id":"303","parent":"300","text":"• Ajustar la terapia antibiótica según los informes de sensibilidad tan pronto como sea posible (n=30).","guid":"QdKJRUlMdW-Iy2fzazGarg","children":[]},{"id":"304","parent":"300","text":"• Cambiar a antibióticos orales si es factible una vez que haya mejoría evidente (n=36).","guid":"0A3W9Iw4LwSTUqqJapsXrA","children":[]}]},{"id":"305","parent":"299","text":"• Cobertura\\Nrequerida:","guid":"oNJnBfWxyeTwflERoFulIQ","children":[{"id":"306","parent":"305","text":"• Cobertura para Gram-negativos: E. coli (más común), Klebsiella spp., Enterobacter spp., Pseudomonas spp.","guid":"InbIIUAGF6UBUKJ_dKnSrA","children":[]},{"id":"307","parent":"305","text":"• Cobertura para anaerobios si se sospecha o identifica una anastomosis biliodigestiva.","guid":"J5haUxqJd4ntUni5dcDtpw","children":[]},{"id":"308","parent":"305","text":"• Considerar cobertura para Enterococcus spp. en infecciones comunitarias\\Nde grado III e infecciones asociadas a la atención de salud.","guid":"PmmMf4QRLl8TZjV-43grVA","children":[]}]},{"id":"309","parent":"299","text":"• Elección del\\Nantibiótico empírico:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"310","parent":"309","text":"• Determinar según:","guid":"9BtNrlLT0FDds9rvovYk4A","children":[{"id":"311","parent":"310","text":"• Infección adquirida en la comunidad o asociada a la atención de salud.","guid":"D0pGIBIb_R1FMXshlFPy-g","children":[]},{"id":"312","parent":"310","text":"• Gravedad de la infección (ver “Grados de severidad”).","guid":"-QzROm98JtVhLiYraK3n_Q","children":[]},{"id":"313","parent":"310","text":"• Patrones de resistencia locales (antibiograma local).","guid":"-o35nDP6CPlGhAfNTnFEbA","children":[]},{"id":"314","parent":"310","text":"• Si se sospecha anastomosis biliodigestiva.","guid":"3RLTzyXVNR-pooQOtRlfvw","children":[]}]},{"id":"315","parent":"309","text":"• Momento de la administración\\Nde antibióticos:","guid":"MKyq6IsgeZ5ZrD4unAKBag","children":[{"id":"316","parent":"315","text":"• Shock séptico: dentro de la primera hora de presentación.","guid":"e93cY4J9Qx0WngQWT9TaDg","children":[]},{"id":"317","parent":"315","text":"• Otros pacientes: dentro de las seis horas de presentación.","guid":"8wswcLKNX9mrvIh4BxIdew","children":[]}]},{"id":"318","parent":"309","text":"• Duración de\\Nla terapia:","guid":"2jrGX8oe7mtY_BBQhj6Z1w","children":[{"id":"319","parent":"318","text":"• Colecistitis aguda grado I y II: hasta 24 hrs después de colecistectomía laparoscópica temprana.","guid":"CtkBh3WyP4c0FIB1hacEOg","children":[]},{"id":"320","parent":"318","text":"• Colecistitis aguda grado III y todas las infecciones colangíticas comunitarias: 4-7 días después de la\\Ncolecistectomía laparoscópica temprana o hasta mejoría sintomática si el paciente se maneja conservadoramente.","guid":"LPEsxwcOx_SnBwOKfUUxkw","children":[]},{"id":"321","parent":"318","text":"• Drenaje urgente de vesícula biliar: continuar\\Nantibióticos por un total de 7 días (n=29).","guid":"-x3En6pQq8ZJxWY5bfInEQ","children":[]},{"id":"322","parent":"318","text":"• Infecciones colangíticas y colecistitis asociadas a la atención de salud\\Ncon bacteriemia grampositiva: considerar 14 días de tratamiento.","guid":"BdWrLaxuDgQq4baFSekErA","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"323","parent":"298","text":"2. Régimen Empírico\\NRecomendado:","guid":"XJLJ10K8T2etkat_vbypzA","children":[{"id":"324","parent":"323","text":"• Infección biliar adquirida\\Nen la comunidad:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"325","parent":"324","text":"• Grado I:","guid":"hoz2lKqLHR3geybJ8GlEZA","children":[{"id":"326","parent":"325","text":"• Cefoxitina.","guid":"Mo8PlDAbv018Fb9tavPKbw","children":[]},{"id":"327","parent":"325","text":"• Moxifloxacina.","guid":"u-TLKLsKKKFNJHwUFmiJUQ","children":[]},{"id":"328","parent":"325","text":"• Ertapenem.","guid":"-R5DH41Uc0FNH2FLbchzew","children":[]},{"id":"329","parent":"325","text":"• Ampicilina-sulbactam (solo si la tasa\\Nde resistencia local < 20%).","guid":"MSZ8jVjqC4k3rRItxjf2ww","children":[]},{"id":"330","parent":"325","text":"• Combinación con metronidazol o\\Nclindamicina + uno de los siguientes:","guid":"ww3h1u9BSXzOd-pMkAha6w","children":[{"id":"331","parent":"330","text":"• Cefazolina.","guid":"OvmSTmJKIPrfmBfA5Vhntg","children":[]},{"id":"332","parent":"330","text":"• Cefuroxima.","guid":"OM4V3-NANeoF6XujYKng0A","children":[]},{"id":"333","parent":"330","text":"• Ceftriaxona.","guid":"AYIHSGh-URd_93mlMJdQ5A","children":[]},{"id":"334","parent":"330","text":"• Cefotaxima.","guid":"2FzPMrflEqSefAa6FIhiuQ","children":[]},{"id":"335","parent":"330","text":"• Ciprofloxacina.","guid":"DT_ETFzUV-7KXFQHUuvf0Q","children":[]},{"id":"336","parent":"330","text":"• Levofloxacina.","guid":"dMNBwsfCr1EzXWBkyGQDTA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"337","parent":"324","text":"• Grado II:","guid":"Jh8mhShQUIYuBn00uJMUxQ","children":[{"id":"338","parent":"337","text":"• Piperacilina-tazobactam.","guid":"ylRUv7uFa46NFVjk4SV1YA","children":[]},{"id":"339","parent":"337","text":"• Moxifloxacina.","guid":"BmZi7u0DiWYzIjRaWBaT-A","children":[]},{"id":"340","parent":"337","text":"• Ertapenem.","guid":"LLFrzVOJaqFBaq4VrocLOw","children":[]},{"id":"341","parent":"337","text":"• Metronidazol + uno\\Nde los siguientes:","guid":"y7RnPWvdL3VGeCR_f7THQg","children":[{"id":"342","parent":"341","text":"• Ceftriaxona.","guid":"G13Q7OdC2VLSfsTcP9lcLg","children":[]},{"id":"343","parent":"341","text":"• Cefotaxima.","guid":"AFZ1fFNYfLS173X9JVBmwA","children":[]},{"id":"344","parent":"341","text":"• Cefepima.","guid":"al17P1gg2bwWHhu3xrXLNA","children":[]},{"id":"345","parent":"341","text":"• Ceftazidima.","guid":"b2QHKMuHOuI2fYiPreVtyQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"346","parent":"324","text":"• Grado III:","guid":"ogIgefEkJeGSJYTa6mIPYg","children":[{"id":"347","parent":"346","text":"• Piperacilina-tazobactam.","guid":"MJH8WLTTBonSPVvE4JOgkg","children":[]},{"id":"348","parent":"346","text":"• Meropenem.","guid":"pd3hkGEuQxgx0gGeKT3N5Q","children":[]},{"id":"349","parent":"346","text":"• Ertapenem.","guid":"UV5FHcMGx_QUiABsCBomJQ","children":[]},{"id":"350","parent":"346","text":"• Imipenem.","guid":"pjzO42XoRRkojP9ztOhJpA","children":[]},{"id":"351","parent":"346","text":"• Metronidazol + uno\\Nde los siguientes:","guid":"2t_GmLHz0tX4J-khDxC5pw","children":[{"id":"352","parent":"351","text":"• Cefepima.","guid":"gcdA54UzQE3MJ7MUuqtISA","children":[]},{"id":"353","parent":"351","text":"• Ceftazidima.","guid":"tj1O8Fxj9QxYVz2ImMjaEA","children":[]},{"id":"354","parent":"351","text":"• Aztreonam.","guid":"iEE16_eWW8-m84ZKpITkIQ","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"355","parent":"323","text":"• Infección biliar asociada a la\\Natención de salud (cualquier grado):","guid":"xk23l-ivjEWzizsFk2Ji-Q","children":[{"id":"356","parent":"355","text":"• Igual que el régimen para infecciones comunitarias de grado III (n=36).","guid":"mCcus2THuiPWzumkDsbSVw","children":[]}]},{"id":"357","parent":"323","text":"• Infección sospechada por\\Norganismos multirresistentes:","guid":"8Dtgl5Dxtxccot4J1d89kg","children":[{"id":"358","parent":"357","text":"• Igual que el régimen para infecciones comunitarias de grado III.","guid":"RyGTSopXVJ6K8SfTjwf1Yg","children":[]},{"id":"359","parent":"357","text":"• Además,\\Nagregar:","guid":"eZ2aoZLh0Wp6LuybSzqg7Q","children":[{"id":"360","parent":"359","text":"• VRE sospechado:","guid":"kk38EhkDTxhN-CsOa3aOhw","children":[{"id":"361","parent":"360","text":"• Linezolid.","guid":"yxV6ZpcXFYtHgPrQhBu6eA","children":[]},{"id":"362","parent":"360","text":"• O daptomicina.","guid":"1H2Zd8t-1xcIOM7Y0fnXoA","children":[]}]},{"id":"363","parent":"359","text":"• MRSA sospechado:","guid":"lLyimu2on_F2WqQz1gjEnA","children":[{"id":"364","parent":"363","text":"• Vancomicina.","guid":"50qBBiSabdjkXtqIPDm1vQ","children":[]}]}]}]}]},{"id":"365","parent":"298","text":"Consideraciones\\NAdicionales:","guid":"0CIPGQhTH1T-69dZUOL8jQ","children":[{"id":"366","parent":"365","text":"• Muchos organismos productores de ESBL son resistentes a fluoroquinolonas.","guid":"tYr0x6XaF6ncNWscxrKArg","children":[]},{"id":"367","parent":"365","text":"• La resistencia de E. coli a ampicilina-sulbactam es cada vez más común, especialmente en América del Norte.\\NConsiderar cuidadosamente las tasas de resistencia locales antes de elegir un régimen antibiótico empírico.","guid":"d6mG6cV98dSDqzUCtUAnMg","children":[]}]}]}]},"node_count":367,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"General","folder":"Entidades clínicas/Cirugía","filename":"Colecistitis aguda-2024","id":"map_338","resolved_references":[]}